### en-US/merchant.ftl
### English (United States) — source locale
###
### This file was scaffolded with:
###   quest gen-l10n examples/localization/merchant.urd --output i18n/en-US/
###
### Fluent features used in this file:
###   { $gold -> [0] … [one] … *[other] … }         — plural selector on numeric var
###   { $item -> [health_potion] … *[other] … }      — item ID → display name
###   { $price }                                     — numeric variable interpolation
###   $has_potion                                    — available but unused here
###                                                    (used as selector in other locales)
###
### Item ID pattern:
###   The urd script passes item = "health_potion" (a slug, never a raw string).
###   Each locale maps the slug to its own display name via a selector.
###   To add a new item: add a new [item_id] arm to every selector in every locale.

